      // refiner, GQA 28q/7kv, 3-axis RoPE) + a Qwen3-VL-8B condition encoder + the FLUX.1 16-channel
      // VAE. Native MLX only (mlx-gen-boogu, no torch backend) → macOnly. True-CFG text-to-image.
